DataCamp Tutorial

Click https://datacamp.com/groups/shared_links/b0d9298dc2e2b1a875975f0151835ef6022aeaea22fe9e96c5ee5eee55f89045 to create your DataCamp account. You must use the provided link as well as your wayne.edu email to join.

When you log in, you will see My Progress on the left. Thats your dashboard where you can track all the assignments and their due dates.

The first assignment is Introduction to R. To start, you can either

  • log into DataCamp, go to your My_Progress, and click the assignment you want to start, or
  • on the course syllabus, click Ex. icon for this weeks module. You will find a direct link to the assignment page on DataCamp. Log in with your DataCamp account and enjoy!
